97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>提示：请确保您已登录客户机操作系统。在客户机中装载虚拟CD驱动器，启动终端，使用tar解压缩安装程序，然后执行vmware-install.pl安装vmware<br>Tools</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>挂载目录</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mount &#x2F;dev&#x2F;cdrom &#x2F;mnt </code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>拷贝</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cp &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;VMwareTools-xxxxxx.tar.gz &#x2F;home</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>进入目录</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cd &#x2F;home</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>取消挂载</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">umount &#x2F;mnt</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>解压</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">tar -zxvf VMwareTools-xxxxxx.tar.gz</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>进入文件</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cd .&#x2F;vmware-tools-distrib  </code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>执行文件</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">.&#x2F;vmware-install.pl</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefin